	<!-- message -->
	<p>I really have no intention of playing WoW, but like most I'm curious.<br />
<br />
Could someone who is playing it please tell me what is the big deal?  Ultimatly, isn't it the same as EQ, you kill stuff, get phat lewt, explore, do a few quests,  make level, get new spells, rinse, spit, repeat?<br />
<br />
I always considered EQ a chat room with a game wrapped around it.  I assume WoW is the same, just with pretty pictures, and a few new bells and whistles.  In the final annalysis, is it REALLY all that different from EQ?<br />
<br />
<br />
Otani</p>
	
	
	
	
	
