	<p>The big difference for me is that Blizzard has a long history of quality, and thusfar they seem to have been able to live up to their name.<br />
<br />
I also think that SOE has tarnished their name by the poor development and support of EQ the last few years and i have no confidence in their products anymore.<br />
<br />
From what little i saw of the beta i can im fond of the atmosphere and overall feel of the environments.<br />
<br />
Cant wait until they release it in europe in January.<br />
<br />
But as with EQ2, WOW might not be appealing to every EQ veteran...</p>
	
	
	
