	<p>Originally I had no plans on buying WoW. I was going to stay in eq till the end but I figured it was worth a look. All I can say is Wow!<br />
<br />
It's like they took everything bad about mmorpg's and threw it out the window. No xp loss when you die. You can't train other people. You can't ks someone elses mob. I could go on an on.<br />
<br />
For the first time in a long time I'm actually having fun. The graphics are well done and doesn't take a super computer to run. I can't say enough good about this game, it's top notch all the way.<br />
<br />
Goodbye EQ, I'm not in your world anymore.</p>
	
	
	
