	<p>WoW to me has been overly simplistic.  The risk to dying is not there.  The rewards for grouping dont seem to be there.<br />
<br />
Its like Blizzard made a game that sole purpose was to give everyone everything they wanted.  In the long run, that tactic will come back and bite em in the ass.<br />
<br />
<br />
As to Blizzard not making a bad product, thats not necessarly true.  Look at both the Diablo 2 expansion and the cesspit known as Battle.Net  The D2 expansion wasnt properly play tested and thus had many xp exploits in it.</p>
	
	
	
