	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>You know, in every WoW thread I've seen the same things said by the WoW fans, and both contradict each other.  In one breath they say how EQ was so bad because "the game doesn't start till XXX level".  But then in another, when an EQ fan says how bored they were with WoW, they say "you weren't high enough level to see what WoW is really like" or "wait till higher levels" etc etc.<br />
<br />
Sorry, but for a game everyone praises as being so great regardless of level, I shouldn't be bored to tears the first few levels.  My first few levels of EQ were FUN!  I didn't reach level 10 for a month or more in EQ and I enjoyed every moment.  I was bored in WOW after the first few hours.  And sorry, telling me to play the game to higher levels to enjoy it just doesn't make sense, I already enjoy a game that you are villainizing for requiring what you are telling me I need to do to enjoy WoW.</p>
	
	
	
