	<!-- message -->
	<p>"I see a lot of tradeskill props in here. None of you wore Tae Ew? Or Valorium Rings of Gallantry? Are you folks telling me there isnt ANY useless tradeskilling in WoW? Come on."<br />
Not if you tradeskill up as you level. Everything is upgrades or useful. For example 12 blacksmithing a stone which has 3 charges of +3 dmg to the weapon you are using. Its much different from other tradeskills, in that its not a labourious affair, and its no fail. Sure, that may take away some of the achievement of it but if you are a real tradeskill junkie you will probably prefer eq2 anyway.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
