	<!-- message -->
	<p>Also, yes I agree with you about the soloing. I think I would prefer it if was more focused around grouping but that doesn't take away from the game, each of the classes are very rewarding.<br />
Pvp, there are pvp servers which are a minority of the servers, however, I believe there is an option of playing pvp later on at the higher levels as a realm vs realm thing, I don't actually think you have to involve yourself in pvp. WoW also has raiding content for those that prefer that.<br />
Its good that you're still enjoying eq, really its just what people prefer to play. I think a lot of people are enjoying the freshness of WoW over eq and its more arguably advanced gameplay.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
